# Domain models

**Product**: id, title, slug, description, images[], categoryId, brand, mrp (paise), sellingPrice (paise), stock, rating, reviewCount, attributes (size/color variants)

**Category**: id, name, slug, parentId (nullable), image

**CartItem**: productId, variantId?, quantity, priceAtAdd (snapshot in paise)

**Order**: id, userId, items[], shippingAddress, status (pending|confirmed|shipped|delivered|cancelled), totalAmount (paise), paymentStatus

**Address**: name, phone, line1, line2, city, state, pincode (6 digits), isDefault

# Business rules

- Store money as integers in paise (₹1 = 100 paise) to avoid float errors
- Discount % = `round((mrp - sellingPrice) / mrp * 100)`
- Cart totals recalculate server-side; never trust client price
- Pincode validates `/^\d{6}$/` for Indian delivery
- Order status transitions are one-way: pending → confirmed → shipped → delivered
